  • Type Parameters:
    K - key type

    public class TripleForLoopTraverser<K>
extends TripleTraverser<K>
    Extracts Embeddings iteratively from a given graph by traversing the graph according to a given TraversalCode. For the iteration the traverser uses a basic for loop.
